SCOPE OF THIS LICENSE (see README "Open-source boundary")

This AGPL-3.0 license covers the OPEN components of Agent Task Market:
  - the REST API / market backend (publish/claim/submit/verify/settle)
  - the credit ledger and settlement logic
  - the MCP server and client SDKs
  - the web UI

It does NOT cover the proprietary risk-engine service (anti-fraud, collusion
detection, Sybil/self-dealing checks, review-sampling rules) or operational
data (reputation graph, treasury state). Those run as a separate closed service
invoked over an internal API and are not distributed under this license.
